              <li><a href="#beveiliging" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">8. Beveiliging van gegevens</a></li>
              <li><a href="#uw-rechten" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">9. Uw rechten</a></li>
